Happy birthday to this beautiful man with the most electric soul ⚡️ 💘

It was one for the ages, folks. Couldn’t be more proud of @ryanvona and the stunning company of @paradebway - it remains one of my very favorite shows ♥️

Spent the night with beautiful people, went to old stomping grounds, and had a Guinness for 🍀 

Photo cred Bruce Glikas @officialbroadwayworld

This one is incredibly special: Janice was a second mother to everyone who knew her. Proud to be part of this concert with these cool people and I really hope to see you there- we’re gonna party hard to make Janice proud!! 💕🌷link in story for tickets or to donate! (100% of ticket proceeds and donations are benefitting the Phyllis Newman Women’s Health Initiative 🎀)
Maisel dump 👒 @maiseltv ep 8 out today! *swipe for the craziest weather moment

Monday night, Waitress Live on Broadway premiered at @tribecafilmfestival and @tsxbroadway - my soul is overflowing with gratitude for getting to be a small slice of this project. I absolutely cannot wait for you all to see this- the film captures the feel of the show in such a magnificent, beautiful way. It couldn’t have happened without so many people, especially the ones in this photo dump 🥧✨

Glam: @essiecohenmakeup 
Dress: @nuuly 
Photos: @eriktanner @garyandrewgershoff

It’s me. Hi. 👋🏻 I’m launching my new coaching website- check it out and if you like what you see, I’d love to work with you! 💕 link in bio/story & message/email me for more info

Headshot by the best @thegingerb3ardmen

There’s been so many ups and downs in the entertainment biz as of late- so we gotta celebrate the wins. The Waitress Musical Live on Broadway is the little film that could, and I hope you get to go see it this December in a movie theater near you. It’s a beautiful couple hours of joy and magic. I’m very proud to have been part of this, and to be able to share it with you all. 
#waitressthemusical

What are you doin’ December 14th?🎶

 Come ring in the holiday season with us at the Bedford Playhouse where we are making our duo-concert debut! We are so excited to have the marvelous @drudin25 joining us on the keys!

So hop on the MetroNorth and meet us under the mistletoe

Tickets are live now- links in bio & story!🎄🎁 🕎 

#broadwayinbedford @bedfordplayhouse

Now that we are fully in the ✨magic✨of the holiday season… ride the train up to beautiful Bedford, NY on Dec 14th for a night of joy 🎄⛄️

@ryanvona and I will be singing and telling stories, and we’d love to see you there! 

Tickets on sale now, link in bio and story!

But only matters what this year we grow.
